<h2 id="guidelines">Guidelines</h2>
<h3 id="title">Crumb order</h3>
<p>The last crumb must represent the current page and should be a span. All other crumbs should be links navigating up the hierarchy. When the user is at the top of the hierarchy, it may or may not make sense to display Breadcrumb.</p>
<h3 id="accessibility">Accessibility</h3>
<p>It is recommended that the last item in the breadcrumb has <code>aria-current="page"</code>.</p>
